"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Unlike centralized account systems, such as cell phone numbers/email/social accounts, DAS offers a decentralized and open sourced approach to account systems. DAS can be used as a digital assets collection account, as an account for accessing general Internet services.\\n\\nLet’s start from registeration!\\n\\nDAS official website: \\n\\n[https://da.systems/](https://da.systems/)\\n\\nClick “Register\\\\\\\\ Manage” button.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/kt5e1dhJx7wwZszs11OEZ.jpg?height=1388&width=2616)\\n\\nThen you need to connect to your wallet. \\n\\nThe wallets currently supporting DAS are imToken, TokenPocket, Math Wallet, Huobi Wallet, Alpha Wallet, HyperPay, Bitkeep Wallet, and more wallets will be connected to the DAS ecosystem in the future.\\n\\nLet’s take Metamask for example.\\n\\nThe next step is to select a register.\\n\\nThere are currently three registrars to choose from: \\n\\n(1) DeName (<https://dename.com/>), a professional third-party account registration service provider that offers decentralized and centralized (email, cell phone number) login and multi-currency payment methods. Unique secondary distribution incentive.\\n(2) GoGoDAS, a third-party service provider that offers decentralized DAS account registration services.\\n(3) DAS, a decentralized DAS account registration service provided by DAS official.\\n\\nThese registers support different kinds of coins for payments.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/uBW-ky-cVh_fgrZdZojnD.png?height=974&width=940)\\n\\nChoose a register and then connect your wallet with a public chain.\\n\\nDAS registration supports using ETH, BSC, Polygon, and Tron public chain addresses.\\nSpecial reminder that although DAS is developed on the Nervos public chain, registration and management with CKB addresses is not yet supported, only payment with CKB is supported.\\n\\nTry different accounts you want to check whether they are available. \\n\\nDAS accounts as a public resource should be avoided to be hoarded by a few people when the social influence is not enough.DAS account registration is opened gradually.\\n\\nWhich accounts can be registered is calculated by a publicly available [algorithm](https://github.com/DeAccountSystems/das-contracts/blob/fca9bfafb79950c7c5d4a86cb379f114b0188ccd/contracts/pre-account-cell-type/src/entry.rs#L579-L584), depending on the account name itself.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/WIdVoNtiRtJ_uHHaF8PpL.png?height=435&width=1816)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/I6lixuAMOOq9eVnBv165_.png?height=1515&width=1430)\\n\\nBesides, in order to prevent malicious use of real brands in the real world, DAS has taken the initiative to set up a reserved list. Users cannot register DAS accounts that are on the reserved list; they can only be claimed by the appropriate organization or individual.\\n\\nYou need CKB to pay for registeration. Click “My” and then go to “Balance”.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/_uDP3_whJN-GeWXVTW3hg.jpg?height=1326&width=1286)\\n\\nIn DAS Balance, you will get your own CKB address. Please click “receive” to see your CKB address.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/7CrzZz3-dkfIgYxp0HsKQ.jpg?height=1422&width=1318)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/n3ve1FY4KUAJfPlRSSjXt.jpg?height=1389&width=1255)\\n\\nYou can buy CKB in CEX such as Binance. Then you can transfer CKB from Binance to your DAS Balance. Then you need to active your CKB in DAS Balance.\\n\\nAfter successful payment, you can manage your DAS account.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/YnvUo4zyk2mTQclTM-AeG.jpg?height=1531&width=1279)\\n\\nYou can modify owner or manager right to other addresses. \\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/QerhXAWE3h2UWyv0tjBy7.jpg?height=1477&width=1309)\\n\\nYou can add new DAS records.\\n\\nChoose “address”, then paste your addresses on different chains, and save these records. Therefore, you have already bound addresses with your DAS account.\\n\\nIn addition, you can choose “profile” and bind accounts on Discord\\\\\\\\ Twitter\\\\\\\\ Telegram and so on. Remeber to save these records.\\n\\nRecords will take few minutes to be saved.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/6aTHuCTLM1KNyMEq7hAJb.jpg?height=1507&width=1280)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/giTyOJFKtrLxks8MZI1vK.jpg?height=1437&width=1256)\\n\\nWe strongly recommand you to set reverse record.\\n\\nYou only need to do once for one DAS account. Set reverse record and save it. Of course you can edit it any time.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/IKAudKsMr2yU8IT3rSvNo.jpg?height=1534&width=1327)\\n\\nEach DAS account has own self page named .bit.cc or .host. It will show all other DAS accounts, NFTs, POAPs under the same address. Feel proud to show off your collection!\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/AhvzftNptXVaifKm8LNwN.png?height=1479&width=2323)\\n\\nJust get a DAS account and begin with it for Web 3.0 world!\\n\\nWish you a wonderful journey in Web 3.0 world with DAS!\",\"timestamp\":1640610959,\"title\":\"Get a DAS account for your Web3.0 journey!\"},\"digest\":\"sf2BJB2mQVHr40j2ahcGqf3XEJLiNzpHAyOaxVQrd5Y\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x5eCBC7E35d03Bfb5310adb50f3208D68E57436F9\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"SHO6_7lVIMlMrm36QstndUYjoQtnAMpY6eXTB5Am51I\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"_4jkr8N3hE9jZzERpfaUNKkgKFvwFFCmESV77RGeG6E\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"tU3734ujsnPdrB9Q63Tlvl2kWJi1c2QHwWfqp2UI2nqMRqBxuWa5ndgsBSms-ll4xruULlNowLOdVMlPQkyq9w\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x50ce7f82542c880f56b4bd28c71ab9fa21dcb9aee27a0f97d79dde984d2b7e71262a256f403a933fe10e358e2f60cf6f676b5734ceafec2165c7ab1f6052269f1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"SHO6_7lVIMlMrm36QstndUYjoQtnAMpY6eXTB5Am51I\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"_4jkr8N3hE9jZzERpfaUNKkgKFvwFFCmESV77RGeG6E\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"sf2BJB2mQVHr40j2ahcGqf3XEJLiNzpHAyOaxVQrd5Y\"}"